init_oa_design_lib(25.10)                            init_oa_design_lib(25.10)

Name
       init_oa_design_lib

Syntax
         init_oa_design_lib <libraryname>

       Type: String

       Default: NULL

       Specifies  the  OpenAccess  design library name to be used. This global
       variable replaces the previous rda_Input(ui_oa_designLib) configuration
       file variable.

Example
              * The following command  specifies  myOALib  as  the  OpenAccess
                database library.

                set init_oa_design_lib {myOALib}

Related Information
              * init_design

